data.title: Lais Ribeiro Reveals Her Glittery Carnaval Makeup Look
data.meta_description:
Brazilian model Lais Ribeiro reveals her go-to Carnaval look, complete with glitter and a feathered headpiece.

Filmed at The Refinery Hotel
